'''林梦县'''（{{lang-ms|Daerah Limbang}}）是[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[砂拉越州|砂拉越州]][[林梦省|林梦省]]的一个[[马来西亚县份|县]]，县府为[[林梦|林梦]]。该县东部和西部与[[文莱|文莱]]接壤，东南部为[[老越县|老越县]]，南部和西南部为[[美里县|美里县]]。由于两侧和海岸被文莱环绕，因此在陆路方面只能通过移民站进入林梦。

==历史==
林梦县原属文莱，1890年被砂拉越第二任拉惹查尔斯·安东尼·约翰逊·布鲁克（Charles Anthoni Johnson Brooke）吞并，成为砂拉越的第五省。汶莱强烈反对吞并。 <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2070.html |title=the CIA World Factbook |access-date=2020-11-14 |archive-date=2011-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514215411/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2070.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

实际的边界沿该地区西侧的[[汶萊河|汶萊河]]与林梦河流域之间的[[分水岭|分水岭]]，并以东侧的邦达鲁安河（Sungai Pandaruan）作为边界。边界协议划定了西部边界<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Land and River Boundary Demarcation and Maintenance – Malaysia's Experience|url=http://www.dur.ac.uk/resources/ibru/conferences/thailand/malaysia.pdf|last=Ahmad Fauzi, Nordin|accessdate=11-04-2008|year=2006|series=Working paper at International Symposium on Land and River Demarcation and Maintenance in Support of Borderland Development|journal=|archive-date=2012-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010220846/http://www.dur.ac.uk/resources/ibru/conferences/thailand/malaysia.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>和邦达鲁安河<ref>"Agreement between the Government of Brunei and the Government of Sarawak regarding the boundary between the States of Brunei and Sarawak between Limbang and Brunei from the coast to a point west of Bukit Gadong signed by the British Resident, Brunei and the Resident, Fifth Division, Sarawak dated 24 February 1933, covering a distance of 37.0 km" quoted by Ahmad Fauzi Nordin".</ref>，而其他边界尚未划定。

[[汶莱|汶莱]]自1967年以来将林梦地区宣称为其领土的一部分（自19世纪80年代以来林梦由白人拉惹吞并后宣称）<ref>{{Cite book|last=R. Haller-Trost|title=The Brunei-Malaysia Dispute Over Territorial and Maritime Claims in International Law|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZMJYOA6g_dYC&pg=PA20|year=1994|publisher=IBRU|isbn=978-1-897643-07-5|pages=20–|access-date=2020-11-14|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116003912/https://books.google.com/books?id=ZMJYOA6g_dYC&pg=PA20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是文莱与马来西亚边境争议的一部分，因为文莱曾经是统一的，但林梦将其的领土分成两半。据文莱媒体报道，该问题已于2009年得到解决。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Brunei drops all claims to Limbang|url=http://www.bt.com.bn/home_news/2009/03/17/brunei_drops_all_claims_to_limbang|accessdate=2013-08-23|author=Ubaidillah Masli|date=2009-03-17|work=[[文莱时报|文莱时报]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712162447/http://www.bt.com.bn/home_news/2009/03/17/brunei_drops_all_claims_to_limbang|archivedate=12-07-2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Border issues between Malaysia, Brunei solved: Official|url=http://en.people.cn/90001/90777/90851/6971863.html|accessdate=2010-05-05|author=张心意|date=04-05-2010|work=[[新华社|新华社]]|publisher=[[人民日报|人民日报]]|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306173819/http://en.people.cn/90001/90777/90851/6971863.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而文莱第二外交和贸易部长[[林玉成_(汶萊)|林玉成]]表示，两国领导人的会议从未讨论过这个问题。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Limbang issue was never discussed: Pehin Dato Lim|url=http://www.bt.com.bn/home_news/2009/03/18/limbang_issue_was_never_discussed_pehin_dato_lim|accessdate=2013-08-23|author=Ubaidillah Masli|date=2009-03-18|work=The Brunei Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140215192853/http://www.bt.com.bn/home_news/2009/03/18/limbang_issue_was_never_discussed_pehin_dato_lim|archivedate=2014-02-15}}</ref>

